David ZINK, petitioner,
v.
Cindy GRIFFITH, Warden, et al. No. 15-5160 (15A59). Supreme Court of the United States July 14, 2015.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice ALITO

*7and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
